[[simple:user:immanuelle/Previous Emperor&#39;s Festival]] [[simple:User:Immanuelle/Previous Emperor's Festival]] [[ja:先帝祭]] [[sn:Previous Emperor Festival]] [[en:Previous Emperor Festival]] [[en:Previous Emperor&#39;s Festival]]
